  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241034.htm", 
  "description": "<b>美国高等法院本周四一致同意，独立于人体的人类基因不允许申请专利。一些医生、病人认为此类专利会妨碍研究、有违医疗操守。在分子医学领域，这将是最有影响力的一个裁定，它决定谁拥有生命的基本结构单位。</b>美国麦利亚德基因公司（&#160;Myriad&#160;Genetics）拥有2项基因相关专利，分别为BRCA1和BRCA2，它可以用来界定女性是否存在患乳腺癌和卵巢癌风险。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d4339d4/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241034.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241034.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241034.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241034.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241034.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsport