 {
  "date": "Fri, 14 Jun 2013 00:18:05 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241033.htm", 
  "description": "<b>视频游戏领域正在酝酿一场白热化的竞争。本周，在美国洛杉矶举办的E3大展上，微软和索尼各自宣布，将在今年推出自己的新一代游戏主机――Xbox&#160;One和PS4的计划，客厅游戏市场激烈的争夺战就此展开。不过，索尼在此次与微软的正面交锋中似乎抢占了先机。</b>本周，微软主要围绕游戏软件进行了介绍，在记者会上，微软介绍了当季即将推出的13款游戏，并宣布Xbox&#160;One将于11月21日上市销售，售价为499美元。上月，微软正式发布Xbox&#160;One，这是其八年内推出的第三代游戏主机，也是其首款全新产品。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d4339d3/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241033.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%BC%A0%E5%A4%B4%E5%AE%A2%E5%8E%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%95%A5%E8%83%9C%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241033.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%BC%A0%E5%A4%B4%E5%AE%A2%E5%8E%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%95%A5%E8%83%9C%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241033.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%BC%A0%E5%A4%B4%E5%AE%A2%E5%8E%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%95%A5%E8%83%9C%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241033.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%BC%A0%E5%A4%B4%E5%AE%A2%E5%8E%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E7%95%A5%E8%83%9C%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal